README for xHub
_______________

English
#######

1) Run Terminal
2) Write: make (You need package: make, g++)
3) Wait ...
4) Now you can start xHub, write "./server" or "./start.sh" for start as deamon
5) The xHub running now :)
6) If you want configure a hub, you must enable show a hidden files
7) Edit a file "config" in folder ".xHub"


